description: Online newspaper based in Chicago Illinois USA
label: The Triibe
title: The_Triibe
exrest: The TRiiBE is an African-American online news and digital media company based in Chicago, Illinois. It was founded in 2017 by Morgan Elise Johnson and Tiffany Walden, along with web developer David Elutilo. In 2019, they published a print version of their TRiiBE Guide, an annual guide to Black Chicago.
